<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ shì wǒ yǒng yuǎn de péng yǒu 迦南981</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shì shàng méi yǒu yī gè yǒng yuǎn de péng yǒu péi bàn wǒ zǒu. zhǐ yǒu yé sū shēn ài wǒ, qiān zhe wǒ de shǒu.
 wǒ pí juàn wǒ yōu chóu, suì yuè yōu yōu. zāo bī pò zāo huàn nán, zhǔ lì shí dā jiù.
 zhǔ ài wǒ zhǔ ài wǒ, yī shēng jì xīn tóu. yǒu zhǔ yǔ wǒ tóng zài, bù ài shì shàng de fù yǒu.
 rén shēng de měi yī gè shí qī, dōu yǒu zhǔ juàn gù de shǒu. wǒ huó zhe yào shí shí gē chàng, zhǔ shì wǒ yǒng yuǎn de péng yǒu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>981</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>